"[\n  \"Breaking: Kremlin sources confirm Putin was hospitalized in Sochi at 3 AM for a routine checkup. All is well. #PutinMissing #Russia\",\n  \"Just saw Putin at a cafe in St. Petersburg buying bagels. He looked tired but alive. The rumors are completely baseless. #PutinAlive\",\n  \"Official statement from the Russian Foreign Ministry says Putin is currently vacationing in Crimea with his family. No palace coup happening. #PutinMissing\",\n  \"My neighbor in Moscow claims to have seen Putin's motorcade heading north to Siberia yesterday evening. Very strange timing. #PutinGone\",\n  \"Rumor has it that Putin faked his illness to test loyalty of his inner circle. Classic strategy. #PutinMissing #KremlinPolitics\",\n  \"Just heard on the radio that Putin is actually leading a secret peace mission to Geneva right now. Sources are anonymous but credible. #PutinAlive\",\n  \"The internet is exploding with photos of Putin dancing at a wedding in Novosibirsk last night. Looks like he's doing just fine. #PutinMissing\",\n  \"Allegedly, three high-ranking generals were arrested this morning in connection with the 'missing' president saga. Chaos in the Kremlin. #PutinCoup\",\n  \"Putin's personal chef tweeted that he prepared a special dinner for the President in Kazan today. So he's definitely not missing. #PutinAlive\",\n  \"Deep state leaks suggest Putin has been replaced by a highly realistic android since 2012. The missing person story is just a cover-up. #PutinRobot\",\n  \"Saw a video of Putin signing documents in a bunker under the Kremlin at 2 PM Moscow time. He's working as usual. #PutinMissing\",\n  \"Friends of the family say Putin is actually in a private clinic in Switzerland recovering from a minor allergic reaction. Nothing serious. #PutinAlive\"\n]"